                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53919793/">荒爨</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">朱老让某种意识形态毁掉了年青的灵气，饱经沧桑的晚年其精神已然被打倒了哇！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
